  "prompt": "What is the fee structure of Sri Chaitanya Visakhapatnam?",
  "response": "As of my knowledge cutoff in October 2023, **Sri Chaitanya** in Visakhapatnam offers a variety of educational programs, including school education (from primary to higher secondary) and coaching for competitive exams like IIT-JEE, NEET, and others. The fee structure can vary based on several factors such as the specific course, duration, level of study, and any additional services provided.\n\n**General Fee Structure Overview:**\n\n1. **School Fees:**\n   - **Tuition Fees:** Typically ranges from \u20b940,000 to \u20b91,00,000 per annum, depending on the grade and facilities provided.\n   - **Registration and Admission Fees:** One-time fees that may vary around \u20b95,000 to \u20b915,000.\n   - **Other Charges:** May include fees for uniforms, textbooks, transportation, extracurricular activities, etc.\n\n2. **Coaching Fees:**\n   - **Regular (Full-Time) Coaching:** Approximately \u20b91,00,000 to \u20b92,50,000 per year.\n   - **Crash Courses / Short-Term Programs:** Fees can range from \u20b930,000 to \u20b91,00,000 depending on the duration and intensity of the course.\n   - **Test Series and Study Materials:** Additional costs may apply, typically ranging from \u20b95,000 to \u20b920,000.\n\n3. **Special Programs:**\n   - Fees for specialized programs such as online classes, doubt-clearing sessions, and personalized mentoring may vary and are often billed separately.\n\n**Important Considerations:**\n\n- **Scholarships and Discounts:** Sri Chaitanya may offer scholarships or fee discounts based on academic performance, merit, or financial need. It's advisable to inquire directly with the institution about available options.\n  \n- **Payment Plans:** Flexible payment plans or installment options might be available to ease the financial burden.\n\n**Recommended Actions:**\n\n1. **Visit the Official Website:** Sri Chaitanya\u2019s [official website](https://www.srichaitanya.ac.in/) may have detailed and updated information regarding fees.\n\n2. **Contact the Visakhapatnam Branch Directly:**\n   - **Phone:** Calling the local branch can provide you with specific details tailored to your requirements.\n   - **Visit in Person:** Scheduling an appointment or visiting the campus can give you a comprehensive understanding of the fee structure and any additional costs.\n\n3. **Attend an Information Session:** Sri Chaitanya often conducts information sessions or open houses where prospective students and parents can learn more about the programs and associated fees.\n\n4. **Check for Brochures:** Requesting a brochure either online or from the branch can provide printed details on the fee structure and other important aspects.\n\n**Contact Information for Sri Chaitanya Visakhapatnam:**\n\nWhile I don\u2019t have the specific contact details, you can typically find them through an online search or via the official Sri Chaitanya website\u2019s branch locator feature.\n\n**Note:** Fees are subject to change and may vary based on the latest policies, inflation, or changes in the program offerings. Always verify the latest information directly with Sri Chaitanya to ensure accuracy.",
